title: Mariposa Market
description: The entire store is certified organic with a large selection of veg and vegan meat alternatives plus local produce, dairy free and gluten free bread, frozen food, dried pasta, a huge bulk staple section (including agave, braggs, shoyu, nuts, grains, cereals), culinary and medicinal herbs (40+ varieties), spices, a small selection of veggie ethnic foods, pet and beauty section. Good stop for grab-and-go type veg and vegan munchy stuff.
